item.title: CVE-2024-27120|2024-08-14T19:56:50.598Z -- celsius%20benelux -- comfortkey
item.description: A Local File Inclusion vulnerability has been found in ComfortKey, a product of Celsius Benelux. Using this vulnerability, an unauthenticated attacker may retrieve sensitive information about the underlying system. The vulnerability has been remediated in version 24.1.2.
